{"tid":2392071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［賤民政策］【再突襲封 3 區】15 歲學生佐敦大廈補習被困 母：又冇被又無盛，要佢瞓地？","createTime":"2021-02-02T14:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T15:59:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea86fd7d6d480fe59b16f6722f1f0f5db0b4638","tid":2392071,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"政府繼昨日封鎖四區後，今日晚上再突襲封鎖佐敦、深水埗及天水圍三區，在各區劃出「受限區域」。其中在佐敦長樂街、志和街一帶封鎖區，居民進入封鎖範圍後，須先登記才可返回住所，但有政府人員不了解居民是否居於受檢區域，要求居民自行確認；亦有 15 歲學生因封區時正在受檢大廈補習，未能離開，媽媽吳女士剛向傳媒大表不滿，「咁細個，一個女仔係入面」、「老師嗰度又冇被又無盛，要佢瞓地呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E7%AA%81%E8%A5%B2%E5%B0%81-3-%E5%8D%80-15-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E8%A3%9C%E7%BF%92%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0-%E6%AF%8D-%E5%8F%88%E5%86%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%88%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%9B-%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%A2%E7%9E%93%E5%9C%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%25B0%2581-3-%25E5%258D%2580-15-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E8%25A3%259C%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0-%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258F%2588%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%259B-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E7%259E%2593%25E5%259C%25B0%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPreoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=842ade5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%25B0%2581-3-%25E5%258D%2580-15-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E8%25A3%259C%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0-%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258F%2588%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%259B-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E7%259E%2593%25E5%259C%25B0%2F&h=10790838\"